# Enables Claude ranking + synthesis. Without it, gttp falls back to a
# deterministic heuristic synthesizer (still produces pages, just less polished).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Live Reddit search needs no credentials: it drives a real Chromium (Reddit
# blocks raw-HTTP clients and gates its OAuth API behind a manual application).
# On a host run, install the browser once with `playwright install chromium`;
# the Docker image bakes it in. A display is required (WSLg provides one; the
# container runs Xvfb).
